morepeople.android.app.core

Class CoreWritablePreferences

  • java.lang.Object
    • morepeople.android.app.core.CoreWritablePreferences
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICoreReadablePreferences, ICoreWritablePreferences

    public class CoreWritablePreferences
extends java.lang.Object
implements ICoreWritablePreferences
    Stores preference values in the shared preferences of the given context. Contract: access to the respective fields ONLY takes place through this class, because it caches values! This means: only ony instance of this class per Context!
